that longitudinal SDCs increase the HLbL contribution by\n$\\Delta a_\\mu^\\text{LSDC}=13(6)\\times 10^{-11}$. This number does not include\nthe contribution from the charm quark, for which we find\n$a_\\mu^{c\\text{-quark}}=3(1)\\times 10^{-11}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 17:49:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 16:01:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
