monium are inside a plasma with finite density. The\ncomplex frequencies obtained are then compared with a Breit Wigner\napproximation for the peaks of the corresponding thermal spectral functions, in\norder to investigate the quantitative agreement of the different descriptions\nof quarkonium quasi-states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 19:46:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2020 13:13:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
