 to discussing the method, and recent results concerning the\nfission dynamics. In addition, we present results on the excitation energy\nsharing between the fragments, which are in agreement with a qualitative\nconclusions extracted from a limited number of experimental measurements of\nproperties of prompt neutrons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 23:51:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
