al arguments are\npresented and discussed in favor of such a scenario for the origin and\nevolution of genetic coding.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 17:47:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 09:08:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-17"}
